Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.90,0:01:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年夏天,美由紀的妹妹在舊校舍被強暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當她被發現時,已經太晚了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.50,0:01:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事件後,舊校舍的門窗都鎖住了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.90,0:01:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺作  \N慘劇一 里香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.90,0:01:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太,這個暑假你要做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.20,0:01:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我去玩,我也只能和其他的男孩一塊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.90,0:02:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,雖然這學校有很多漂亮的女孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錢,也只能在家看電影…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.30,0:02:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,健太,是黃色電影嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.35,0:02:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我可以到你家去和你一起看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!我必須要自己先看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.12,0:02:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那樣說嘛!今晚我們一定能一起好好快樂的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開,噁心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你們的關係真好啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒! 還有琴末 !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能聽到你們的談話!對嗎?琴末 !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.90,0:02:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然健太的家裡有很多黃色電影和錄像帶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在琴末 面前說那樣的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…你把琴末 想像成黃色電影的女主角嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.10,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,不是…琴末,請相信我,我不是那樣的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.50,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,遺作,不要用那種眼神看著琴末 !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是變態!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.01,0:04:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舊校舍美由紀的妹妹被強暴 是你幹的吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美由紀小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴末,我買了輛新車.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天去兜風!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？宗光,我可以一起去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.90,0:04:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我明天和你們一起去!\N讓琴末和你單獨一起太危險了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.90,0:04:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分呢,這麼不相信我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…真是個噁心的人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗光是全校女生的偶像呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去唱卡拉OK吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿,看這邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香…和美由紀!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個"討厭男人的美由紀"也會和我們一起去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會了,我只是和里香一起去而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都可以,就和我們一起去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼說,健太?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的,里香就和我們一起去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,決定了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天1點鐘在車站集合！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事你真是熱心啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美老師,請不要打擾他,這很麻煩的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會,明美,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先說明,他不喜歡你的態度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有必要說到這種地步…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.49,0:05:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和久美老師沒什麼關係!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我先走了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在看什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,久美老師!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是!但真是不錯的內褲啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個老太婆的內褲這麼好看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.90,0:06:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼,明美?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.68,0:06:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢,有兩個男孩喜歡妳呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明美,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看呢,明美和久美老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.90,0:07:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在別說那個,看這個,乳房和屁股,哦,我再也受不了了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,照相機在哪兒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在修理中!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,健太,看看那邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是遺作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰它!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色老頭,滾出去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.90,0:07:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,不要這麼生氣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在看明美的身材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看起來有個不錯的身材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.93,0:07:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我想要摸摸看,脫掉你的衣服!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像個超級模特兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在讚美嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在別人面前說那種話!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次,我會只對你說的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經常像那樣說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實話說,這是第一次!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太,那是什麼?難不成是…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道才怪,你這傢伙…借我看一下吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,我都還沒看呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會告訴你的,再見!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,等等,健太!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是薄情的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.90,0:08:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午5點鐘,在舊校舍的音樂教室等我…嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.00,0:08:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在女生中出名了,請原諒我,陣八!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要尋找自己的幸福!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.90,0:09:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這看起來不像是偽造或者開玩笑的信!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噁心的老頭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.10,0:09:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好陰森恐怖的地方啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦!是這兒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是大家都在這兒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.00,0:10:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人叫我來這兒的,是你嗎,健太?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這兒是因為這封信!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們的一樣.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是健太寫的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是健太寫的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要做這種事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.43,0:10:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.90,0:10:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美由紀…和陣八？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們都在這兒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.19,0:10:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你的原因一樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.66,0:10:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你也收到了那封信?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.77,0:10:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.00,0:11:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太!快點招了吧,做這種事的人是你對吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當進來的時,有看到那老頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺作?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是遺作,我也有看到!但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,好可怕呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢,我們回家吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒時間和你們玩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,別開玩笑了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊,是里香啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜健太你想約我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,里香…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.90,0:12:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會高潮的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香 !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該過走了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,明天唱完卡拉OK後吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.90,0:13:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,老師…有一點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要上廁所!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,小心點喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.90,0:13:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.68,0:13:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊,被鎖死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧,讓我來試試!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的鎖了,打不開了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.35,0:13:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了,找找其他出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.91,0:13:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的,我們分頭去找!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.80,0:13:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.90,0:14:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太,這樣做我好害羞啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼濕了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香…不行啊 這樣做的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.40,0:15:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太,健太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快受不了了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.90,0:15:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,請和做愛!請和我做愛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.90,0:15:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗光,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.08,0:15:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊,出去的路全被封死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我們真的被困在這兒了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.57,0:16:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能,一定有其他離開的方法!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.90,0:16:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.99,0:16:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.00,0:16:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且,里香去上廁所也還沒回來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.54,0:16:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師,你為什麼不和她一起去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣八!我們要找到里香 !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們兩個了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美老師,別那麼擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能找到的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.90,0:16:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我們走了!也會把健太找回來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.90,0:16:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,所有出口都被釘死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一卷錄像帶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"請大家一起看,遺作!"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是遺作啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛,對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的陰部露出來了喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是誰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唷,里香,妳覺得如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.18,0:17:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣八!為什麼?那麼,這人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人!宗光!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.90,0:18:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?快放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們,救救我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.90,0:18:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼,你告訴我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.70,0:18:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡看起來很想要,不是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,住手…宗光!不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.50,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你,不要這樣…不行~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.90,0:18:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過分!好過份…饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.10,0:18:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你幫幫我,陣八!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要照到宗光的臉喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.90,0:18:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧,我的臉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要殺我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死!請別殺我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的!妳會聽話了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.06,0:19:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好女孩,那麼你再說一次在廁所裡說過的話!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.48,0:19:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,放開我,放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼濕了,還說不出口嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.20,0:19:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛,不要拉,請不要拉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你想說了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香的…那裡…做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.60,0:19:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不見!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.90,0:19:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香是個淫賤的女人,所以和我做愛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.70,0:20:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?妳想做愛啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個騷貨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所願,我就幹妳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.90,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有女人都是騷貨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在,我們就來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個淫亂,騷貨…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,宗光!已經夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好難受…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.64,0:21:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香還想要更多處罰對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.78,0:21:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香是壞孩子,再多欺負我一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.55,0:21:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,那樣健太會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.15,0:21:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,不是和健太卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.40,0:21:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我…啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺作這混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.10,0:22:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個變態!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.77,0:22:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美老師,我們現在該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.99,0:22:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…你問我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.31,0:22:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太,剛才你在哪兒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.40,0:22:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.67,0:22:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你發現這錄像帶的吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.40,0:22:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,我在走廊發現的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.40,0:22:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然這個真是巧合呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.40,0:22:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才出去了很久!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.65,0:22:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗光,你想要說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.75,0:22:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這捲帶子,是你拍的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.80,0:22:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.99,0:22:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,說不定真的是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.90,0:22:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.26,0:22:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,健太!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.27,0:23:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!陣八!放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.40,0:23:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太,我聽某人說你收集黃色電影!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣八,你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.40,0:23:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.80,0:23:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為那個愚蠢的遺作能做出這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.40,0:23:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為健太你和遺作一起幹的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.40,0:23:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說,宗光!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.40,0:23:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說清楚,宗光!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.40,0:23:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太愛里香 了,所以你就強暴她了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.90,0:23:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗光,你這傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.56,0:23:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.30,0:23:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,他這樣說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.20,0:23:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前開始就覺得你不對勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.20,0:23:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗光和健太在這種時候別吵架了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.20,0:23:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯!真不愧是老師,另眼相看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.40,0:23:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣,大家就別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.57,0:23:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找里香 !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.40,0:23:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?等等,美緒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.40,0:24:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們在這裡的時,不知道遺作又要對里香做什麼了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒,不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.30,0:24:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止她,快阻止她,現在跑出去的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.80,0:24:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師,冷靜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.80,0:24:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,陣八!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.60,0:24:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家,待在這兒不要出去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.97,0:24:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,遺作這混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.80,0:24:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把里香藏在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.40,0:24:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香 !
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.40,0:24:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你聽到,回答我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.60,0:24:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太,你走這邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.87,0:24:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.10,0:24:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.40,0:25:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解的,久美老師!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.99,0:25:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.00,0:25:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,只會說那種不負責任的話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.40,0:25:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在這兒等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.40,0:25:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.40,0:25:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開,我要回家!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.30,0:25:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿妳沒辦法,只有這次喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.50,0:25:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,究竟把里香藏到哪裡了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.51,0:25:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是遺作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.90,0:26:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽到什麼聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:10.90,0:26:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.40,0:26:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一集完!
